s and nothing else. But there is so much more to [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://conversationpublicrelations.com/2008/12/10/wordpress-27-coletrane-released/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 “Coletrane” released | Conversation Public Relations</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22505\">\r\n	<p>[...] 2.7 kısa bir süre önce yayınlandı. Yeni sürümde ilk göze çarpan yenilik yeni arayüz [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://offchu.kptngl.net/wordpress-27-coltran/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” | offlog</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22506\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] @ WordPress.org  addthis_url = ‘http%3A%2F%2Fwww.techau.tv%2Fblog%2F%3Fp%3D861′; addthis_title = [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.techau.tv/blog/?p=861\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">techAU » Blog Archive » WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” Released !!</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22507\">\r\n	<p>[...] seen my wordpress admin dashboard showing “WordPress 2.7 Coltrane” and I followed the link to know that WordPress 2.7 version is available for download now. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.problogineer.com/wooha-wordpress-27-is-out-there\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Wooha - WordPress 2.7 Is Out There !!</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22508\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] Read about the release here: <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/</a>. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://patrickdevivo.com/2008/12/ahh-wordpress-27-is-here/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Ah WordPress 2.7 is Here | Patrick DeVivo dot com</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"c