back from <a href=\"http://djupiter.web.ugm.ac.id/wp/internet/freebies/wordpress-27-code-name-coltrane/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 Code Name “Coltrane” - The Cyber Journey</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22624\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress 2.7 codename “Coltrane” is out now! You can get it right here. You can read the announcement by Matt here. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.khimhoe.net/2008/12/11/wordpress-27-%e2%80%9ccoltrane%e2%80%9d/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” | KhimHoe.Net</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22625\">\r\n	<p>[...] dem Spitznamen “Coltrane” ist heute in den frühen Morgenstunden die Version 2.7 von WordPress erschienen. Ein Schwerpunkt der neuen Version ist das komplett neu gestaltete Backend und die Möglichkeiten [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.svenkubiak.de/2008/12/11/wordpress-27-erschienen/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 erschienen | svenkubiak.de</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22626\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] se ha lanzado la versión definitiva de WordPress 2.7, incluye multitud de novedades, la más aparente es el cambio de interfaz en el [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://estebansaiz.com/blog/2008/12/11/wordpress-27-coltrane/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 Coltrane lanzado con muchas novedades | Mareos de un Geek</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22627\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress, akhirnya, pada hari ini Automattic telah pun mengeluarkan versi terbaru WordPress, iaitu WordPress 2.7 dengan nama kod Coltrane (John Coltrane). Antara perkara utama yang diubah dalam WordPress 2.7 [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://amanz.my/2008/758/amanz-kini-menggunakan-wordpress-27/\" rel=\