ll ‘bugs’ [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.felipe1982.com/blog/2008/12/12/wordpress-blog-updated-to-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">felipe1982’s useless blog about nothing » Blog Archive » WordPress Blog Updated to 2.7</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22828\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] This is a MAJOR upgrade from previous versions, and you can read all about the new features here. Needless to say, this is a pretty big [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.zanderchance.com/2008/12/11/wordpress-27-released/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 Released! » Zander Chance</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22829\">\r\n	<p>[...] what WordPress Blog say about wordpress 2.7 with a video of new features   December 11, 2008 | Filed Under Web [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.nitinjain.org/2008/12/wordpress-27-now-available/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 Now Available : Nitin Jain</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22830\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] hij is er: WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” het nieuwste kindje in de WordPress familie. De ontwikkelaar hebben er maanden aangewerkt maar dat [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.eelcomartens.nl/twee-punt-zeven\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">2.7 | Eelco\'s Wereldje</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22831\">\r\n	<p>[...] has just announced the official release of version 2.7&nbsp; (codenamed Coltrane) of their blogging / content-management system. I’ve [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.steve-c.co.uk/2008/12/11/wordpress-27-officially-released/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Steve’s Space » Blog Archive » WordPress 2.7 Officially Released</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li