11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22870\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] 大家所期待的 WordPress 2.7 終於發佈了!! WordPress 2.7 Coltrane 正式發佈了，這次的改版有著全新的登入管理介面，讓使用者有全新的視覺感受。 [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://61.218.231.239/wordpress/?p=73\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 正式版發佈了，全新的登入管理介面!! « 大雄寶店</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22871\">\r\n	<p>[...] Reader more [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.livecrunch.com/2008/12/11/wordpress-27-coltrane-has-been-released-today/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 Coltrane Has Been Released Today</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22872\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] 2.7 was released yesterday, and like a lot of people I upgraded by blog. &nbsp;Upgrading was a massive pain as usual, but [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.wizardstower.co.uk/wordpress/2008/12/11/upgraded-to-wordpress-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Upgraded to WordPress 2.7 | Wizard\'s Blog</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22873\">\r\n	<p>[...] a big congratulations! to the WordPress Team!&nbsp; Here’s their write-up on the release.&nbsp; They’ve worked really hard, and I’m jazzed to see what all it holds.&nbsp; I’ll be [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.whypad.com/posts/congrats-to-wordpress-team-27-coltrane-is-here/445/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Congrats to WordPress Team - 2.7 “Coltrane” is Here » WhyPad</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22874\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] Enlace: WordPress [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://el-nerdvana.com/?p=152\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">El Nerdvana</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22875\">\r\n	<p>[...] a comment »  A big day today for WordPress: The eagerly awaited 2.7 release was officially released this morning and lots of people are downloading [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://toni.org/2008/12/11/wordpress-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 « toni.org</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22876\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] Najbolj opazna razlika je popolnoma nova tema za administracijo. Dodali so tudi avtomatično updejtanje, threaded comments in še veliko več. Preberite uraden wordpress blog post. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.bloganje.com/wordpress-27-je-tu.html\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 je tu! | Bloganje.com</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22877\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” The first thing you’ll notice about 2.7 is its new interface. From the top down, [they’ve] listened to [our] feedback and thought deeply about the design and the result is a WordPress that’s just plain faster. Nearly every task you do on your blog will take fewer clicks and be faster in 2.7 than it did in a previous version. (Download it now, or read on for more.) [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://archshrk.com/2008/12/time-to-ride-the-coltrane\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Time to ride the Coltrane | archshrk</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22878\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] ver la historia de esta versión de WordPress llamada “John Coltraine” en este post, de paso siquieres allí puedes bajar esta [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://hiperterminal.novenopiso.org/2008/11/13/probando-wordpress-27-beta-2/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Probando WordPress 2.7 Beta 2 | Hiperterminal</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22879\">\r\n	<p>[...] La nouvelle version de WordPress, la 2.7 (dédiée au grand sax