 Het upgraden van de 2.6 versies is een fluitje van een cent, oftewel [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.onbezet.nl/2008/12/11/wordpress-27-%e2%80%9ccoltrane%e2%80%9d/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” » Onbezet.nl</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22913\">\r\n	<p>[...] new version of WordPress was released last night, dubbed 2.7 “Coltrane”, and it’s one of the largest updates the blogging platform has seen to date. The dashboard [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://patrickmaloney.net/index.php/2008/12/11/wordpress-27-release/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 Release - PmNet Aggregator</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22914\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] hab ich den Blog auf WordPress 2.7 updated, was eine komplett neue Admin-Oberfläche miteinschließt. Sieht nun nicht nur schicker, [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://blog.roleplaytalk.net/2008/12/11/blog-facelifting/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Roleplaytalk Blog » Blog Archive » Blog Facelifting</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22915\">\r\n	<p>[...] the release of &nbsp; WordPress 2.7 i upgraded quickly to this version. The famous quick install only took 3 minutes and i encountered [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.lacisoft.com/blog/2008/12/11/running-on-wordpress-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Running on WordPress 2.7</a> on December 11, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-22916\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] Genbeta | Un vistazo a WordPress 2.7 Enlace | Anuncio del lanzamiento en el blog oficial Descarga | WordPress [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://miranda23.wordpress.com/2008/12/11/wordpress-27-ya-disponible-oficialmente/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 ya disponible oficialm