ed! | Resource Pile</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23010\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress 2.7 Coltraneがドロップダウンしました。ダッシュボードも2.5、2.6などよりもかなり使いやすくデザインが変更。解析機能であるBlogstatも備わり(ただし、Wordpress.comでBlogを持っていることが前提/ユーザー名、パスワードが要求されるため)、メディア インサートがWordpress2.6と比べてページ変遷して使いにくくなった感がある。いつものように使えなくプラグインがあるので導入する前にチェックの必要あり。 [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.collisiondurythme.com/wordpress-2-7-coltrane\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Collision du rythme » WordPress 2.7 Coltrane リリース</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23011\">\r\n	<p>[...] [From WordPress › Blog » WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane”] [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.b12partners.net/wp/2008/12/11/installed-wordpress-27-coltrane/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Installed WordPress 2.7 Coltrane at B12 Solipsism</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23012\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] yaitu Worpress 2.7. WordPress 2.7 tersebut diberi nama Coltrane. Dalam Blog WordPress dengan judul WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” dikatakan bahwa WordPress 2.7 lebih cepat dibanding versi sebelumnya. Dan juga dikatakan akan [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://170869.com/wordpress-27-stabil.htm\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 Stabil | August 17th, Birth with Freedom</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23013\">\r\n	<p>[...] visiting!Semalam saya melakukan upgrade WordPress saya ke versi terbaru 2.7 yang diberi nama kode Coltrane. Kalau melihat admin pagenya yang familiar kaya web 2.0 sehingga sangat mudah untuk digunakan dan [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.santoslolowang.com/tips/upgrade-wordpress-ke-versi-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">www.santoslolowang.com » Upgrade wordpress ke versi 2.7</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23014\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] very well done, and with Coltrane, they called it, what should we need more than this open-source (free) blogging system which look [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.wikusama.com/2008/12/12/wordpress-27-is-out/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Ikatan Alumni SMK Telekomunikasi Malang » Blog Archive » WordPress 2.7 is Out</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23015\">\r\n	<p>[...] sum up how different WordPress 2.7 from previous releases of the blogging software, founder Matt Mullenweg said: The changes to WordPress in 2.5 and 2.7 were necessary for us to break free of much of the [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.rotorblog.com/2008/12/11/wordpress-prepares-platform-for-its-transformation-to-a-social-network/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress Prepares Platform for its Transformation to a Social Network</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23016\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] mas detalles visitar WordPress    Archivo en : Desarrollo Web  Comentarios :  [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://blog.indatcom.net/2008/12/11/wordpress-27-liberado/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Blog InDatcom » WordPress 2.7 liberado</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23017\">\r\n	<p>[...] about the new version can be seen here, and even more about the new release can be read on the WordPress Dev&nbsp;Blog.  There are currently no comments highlighted.SHARETHIS.addEntry({ title: “WordPress 2.7 has [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://toastedsourdough.com/asides/wordpress-27-has-arrived\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 has&nbsp;arrived | SourDough2.0</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23018\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] tidsdödare har jag nu uppdaterat WordPress till version 2.7. Vid första anblick ser adminsidan helt annorlunda ut och är mer anpassningsbar än tidigare. En [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://huvudfoting.com/webblogg/2008/12/12/i-vantan-pa-att-lagga-mig/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Daniels webblogg » I väntan på att lägga mig</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23019\">\r\n	<p>[...] As the title says it all. I’m&nbsp;obsessed with WordPress more after the launch of 2.7. The new Admin UI and features are just great. &nbsp;What I like the most in new WordPress is the updation of plugins &amp; WordPress. This will probably be the last time I upgraded my blog manually. Now whenever WordPress have updates to install, I’m just two-click away  – awesome. &nbsp;Wanna know more about the new WordPress 2.7, click here. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://teabreak.pk/wordpress-2-7-and-i-m-loving-it-35/9867/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 and I’m Loving It | Tea Break</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23020\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] As the title says it all. I’m&nbsp;obsessed with WordPress more after the launch of 2.7. The new Admin UI and features are just great. &nbsp;What I like the most in new WordPress is the updation of plugins &amp; WordPress. This will probably be the last time I upgraded my blog manually. Now whenever WordPress have updates to install, I’m just two-click away  – awesome. &nbsp;Wanna know more about the new WordPress 2.7, click here. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://teabreak.pk/wordpress-2-7-and-i-m-loving-it-35/9867/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 and I’m Loving It | Tea Break</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23021\">\r\n	<p>[...] Coltrane, is a JAZZ artist, and his name was chosen to be WordPress 2.7 latest release, Coltrane. Coltrane inspired many other generations of artists with his music, and I really like [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://br.bingorabbit.com/2008/12/coltrane/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Coltrane | Ibrahim Abdel Fattah Mohamed Personal bLOG</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23022\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] (vandaag, eigenlijk) is WordPress 2.7 eindelijk gereleased. Ik had al een tijdje een test-opstelling om te zien of er grote problemen te voorzien waren met [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://doenietzomoeilijk.nl/archief/wordpress-27-firefox-31-en-de-nieuwe-dnzm-lay/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7, Firefox 3.1 en de nieuwe DNZM-lay - Doe Niet Zo Moeilijk!</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23023\">\r\n	<p>[...] Categorías:Actualizaciones, CMS, WordPress    Tras un largo período de espera, se encuentra disponible la versión 2.7 del exitoso CMS WordPress. Como ya se ha mencionado antes, su principal característica es su nueva interfaz, un diseño simplemente más rapido. Casi todas las tareas que usted haga en un blog WordPress 2.7, tendrá un menor número de clics y será más rápido que en una versión anterior.  Tambien cabe destacar las nuevas características implementadas sutilmente a través de la nueva interfaz: el nuevo dashboard que se puede organizar con arrastrar y soltar para poner las cosas más importantes en la parte superior, QuickPress, paginación, y la capacidad de respuesta a los comentarios de tu escritorio, la capacidad de instalar cualquier plugin directamente desde WordPress.org con un solo clic.   En conclusión, esta grandiosa versión ya está disponible para su descarga directa. También ya está la versión oficial en español, de parte de los mismos desarroladores, para que disfrutes de esta nueva versión de WordPress.   Fuente: wordpress.org [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://cmstecno.com/disponible-para-la-descarga-wordpress-27\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Disponible para la descarga WordPress 2.7</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23024\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] vídeo oficial mostra tudo em detalhes e faz uma comparação bem adequada entre a improvisação do jazz e as [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.ronaldocamacho.com.br/wordpress-27-coltrane-o-nome-ja-diz-a-importancia-da-versao/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 Coltrane - O nome já diz a importância da versão | Blog do Ronaldo</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23025\">\r\n	<p>[...] out that video and WordPress.org for more [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://technstuff.com/news/general/wordpress-27-is-out/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 is Out! | techNstuff</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23026\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] was excited about WordPress 2.7 from the day I heard about it. Got myself involved in testing nightly builds and user testing. But [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.gnetiks.com/gblog/?p=482\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Giri’s Blog » Blog Archive » WordPress Coltrane</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23027\">\r\n	<p>[...] подробнее, на английском [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://topproblog.com/wordpress-27-finalnaya-versiya-%e2%80%9ccoltrane%e2%80%9d/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 финальная версия - “Coltrane” | Лучшее про Блоги</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23028\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] Announced today on the WordPress development blog, 2.7 incorporates a major UI rewrite, which has undergone extensive usability testing, as well as good old fashioned crowdsourced input. Over 150 people contributed to its development, and this is one of the most well publicized releases of WordPress ever. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://ayvegh.wordpress.com/2008/12/11/wordpress-27-coltrane-is-here/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” is here! « ayvegh’s blog</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23029\">\r\n	<p>[...] finished upgrading all the blogs to WordPress 2.7. Very nice. I love the new admin interface. It is far an away less cluttered. I’m writing [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://konicki.com/blog2/2008/12/11/just-upgraded/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Just upgraded | Deacon\'s Blog</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23030\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] no sooner do I have a bunch of new stuff added to the blog, than WordPress releases version 2.7. This is no small release. There are a bunch of things added that can break plugins and themes. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.cyberward.net/blog/2008/12/wordpress-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Cyberward.net » Blog Archive » WordPress 2.7</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23031\">\r\n	<p>[...] official WordPress 2.7 code name “Coltrane” has been released. Congratulations to the WordPress development team on another successful [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://brolly.ca/blog/wordpress/congrats-wordpress-27-officially-released/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Congrats! WordPress 2.7 Officially Released › Brolly</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23032\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] avui tenim ja disponible la nova versió de WordPress 2.7 per als nostres blocs [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.carmepla.com/cat/2008/12/12/misty-look-funciona-amb-wordpress-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Misty Look funciona amb WordPress 2.7 | El bloc de Carme Pla</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23033\">\r\n	<p>[...] Check the Introduction to WordPress 2.7 Video at Official WordPress 2.7, codenamed “Coltrane” blog. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.niharsworld.com/2008/12/12/wordpress-27-%e2%80%9ccoltrane%e2%80%9d-is-released/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">rdpress 2.7 “Coltrane” is released! | Nihar\'s World</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23034\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] site and (most) all of my others are now proudly sporting WP 2.7! I hard-lined my notebook to the router to get the upgrades done (sometimes wireless just [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://andanything.com/models-mayhem-upgrades\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Models, mayhem, and upgrades - And Anything</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23035\">\r\n	<p>[...] Neustart mit WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.svenrabe.com/wordpress-27.php\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 « Blog von Sven Rabe</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23036\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] | Anuncio del lanzamiento en el blog oficial Descarga | WordPress [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://malwares.phpnet.us/wordpress-27-en-espanol-a-la-carta/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Foro contra Malwares » WordPress 2.7 en español a la carta</a> on December 12, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23037\">\r\n	<p>[...] salio (AL FIN!) la version tan esperada de WordPress, 2.7. A esta le pusieron Coltrane. Bueno, los que no tienen WP, no les voy a enumerar las caracteristicas u.u, pero meto este video, [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://microutopia.com.ar/2008/12/11/wordpress-27-final/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" clas