s 2.7 - Disponible | Power</a> on December 15, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23311\">\r\n	<p>[...] You can read more about the release an the WordPress Development Blog. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://jkamp.com/?p=172\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Josh Kampmeier » Blog Archive » WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” - WOW!</a> on December 15, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23312\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] oczekiwana wersja WordPress’a o numerku 2.7 pojawiła się 11 grudnia, ale ja dopiero dzisiaj znalazłem czas na aktualizację [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://blog.tobiasz.org/2008/12/aktualizacja-wordpress-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Arkadiusz Tobiasz » Archiwum » Aktualizacja: WordPress 2.7</a> on December 15, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23313\">\r\n	<p>[...] has released the new version of its CMS 2.7 “Coltrane”. I have tried it already, and all seems to be running well. Even the compatibility with earlier [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.cyberfootprint.eu/weekly-cyberfootprints-dec-16-2008/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Weekly CyberFootprints - Dec 16 2008 | CyberFootprint</a> on December 16, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23314\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] Sortie de WordPress 2.7 via Amaury &amp; WordPress [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.spawnrider.net/blogs/2008/12/16/les-billets-de-la-semaine-20/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Les billets de la semaine #20 | Le blog de Yohann CIURLIK | Spawnrider.Net :: Blog</a> on December 16, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23315\">\r\n	<p>[...] particularly happy that this time I will be running on the spanking new jazz inspired ‘Coltrane‘ (a.k.a WordPress 2.7). It’s also a great coincidence that Automatic made [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.anibeagamah.