, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23338\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] can be dragged and dropped in any number of arrangements. I’ve included the video from WordPress themselves illustrating some of this new flexibility [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.search-placement.com/blog/general/the-new-wordpress-coltrane-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">The New WordPress: Coltrane (2.7) :: Search Engine Placement</a> on December 16, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23339\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.collegemediainnovation.org/blog/2008/12/16/links-for-2008-12-16/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">links for 2008-12-16 – Innovation in College Media</a> on December 16, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23340\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] Por supuesto, WordPress 2.7 [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://elreplicante.es/traca-de-links\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Traca de links - El replicante</a> on December 16, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23341\">\r\n	<p>[...] For more on WordPress 2.7, check out the little video they put together highlighting all the fun stuff in this new release here. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.lilaccreative.com/2008/12/wordpress-27-is-available/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Lilac Creative » WordPress 2.7 is Available!</a> on December 16, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23342\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] main reason om naar een andere template voor mijn weblog te kijken was het feit dat WordPress 2.7&nbsp;, waar dit weblog mee gemaakt is, is uitgebracht. Met nieuwe features die een aangepaste layout [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://ronsrace.nl/2008/12/wennen/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Wennen? » Ron’s Race</a> on December 16, 2008</cit