3356\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress 2.7更新在幾天前發佈了。原本我沒有打算升級，因為覺得追更新實在是蠻麻煩的。不過在我看到官網上的介紹影片後，馬上就去下載了。因為2.7的新介面實在是太棒了。 [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.codacoza.com/usability/wordpress-27%e7%9a%84%e6%96%b0%e4%bb%8b%e9%9d%a2/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Coda.Coza | xhtml, css, IE有問題！ » WordPress 2.7的新介面</a> on December 17, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23357\">\r\n	<p>[...] örülnék, ha a mentések készítése is kicsit egyszerűbb lenne… További részletek a bejelentésben, amiben egy kis videót is közzétettek az új kiadás újdonságairól. Címkék: [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://kobra.hu/?p=250\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">K:logger » Blog Archive » WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane”</a> on December 17, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23358\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress 2.7 – (Coltrane) – vyšel minulý týden. Upgrade bez problémů, příjemná je nová administrace, možnost přetahovat jednotlivé bloky, nově je tu automatický upgrade pluginů i programu, lepší stránkovatelné komentáře, zvýraznění příspěvku na hlavní stránce, atpd. Můžete se opět podívat.      Publikační systémyPublikační systémyPublikační systémy – Simple PHP Blog (čeština)Publikační systémy – EasyBlog I.Publikační systémy – EasyBlog II.Publikační systémy – EasyBlog III.Publikační systémy – EasyBlog IV.Publikační systémy – EasyBlog V.Publikační systémy – LoudblogPublikační systémy – PPWizardPublikační systémy – WordPressPublikační systémy – Nucleus CMSPublikační systémy – BLOG:CMSPublikační systémy – EasyBlog v LinuxuPublikační systémy – WordPress 2.6Publikační systémy – WordPress 2.7 [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://phirebase.com/publikacni-systemy-wordpress-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Publikační systémy - WordPress 2.7 | Phirebase</a> on December 17, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23359\">\r\n	<p>[...] <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/</a> [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.openracoon.org/?p=151\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Funny Face » Blog Archive » WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane”</a> on December 17, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23360\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress 2.7 ‘Coltrane”, begitulah rilis ini diberi nama. Saya sendiri tidak mengerti kenapa rilis WordPress selalu menggunakan nama legenda musik jazz untuk setiap rilis mereka. Mungkin karna Matt begitu fanatik dengan musik jazz. Klo semua nama legenda musik jazz sudah habis dipake semua kira-kira gimana yah? Yang membuat saya terheran-heran sebenarnya adalah rilis ini hanya berselang satu hari dari rilis WordPress 2.7 Release Candidate 2! Koq cepet sekali yah. Ckckck. Saya tidak perlu berpanjang lebar lagi menjelaskan fitur-fitur apa saja yang sudah ditanamkan di rilis ini. Nah, sekarang cuma sedikit memberikan review (karna jarang ngeblog) setelah menggunakannya beberapa bulan ini yang tiada hari tanpa upgrade itu. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://blog.anomali.net/2008/12/11/wordpress-27-is-officially-released/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 is Officially Released » Anomali.net</a> on December 17, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23361\">\r\n	<p>[...] el motivo de que los de WordPress.org por fin sacaron la versión 2.7, decidí borrar todo y volver a empezar. Un nuevo tema (para variar), nuevas ideas y pronto mucho [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.jrodas.com/2008/12/estrenemos-wordpress-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Estrenemos WordPress 2.7 « Jrodas.com</a> on December 17, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23362\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] 2.7, giving us lots of new features like easy implementation of sticky posts (the latest TANcast will always be the first thing you see [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://tancast.com/2008/12/17/coming-soonish/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Coming Soonish… | TANcast</a> on December 17, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23363\">\r\n	<p>[...] νέο WordPress 2.7 αποτελεί σημαντική αναβάθμιση για το Admin Panel αλλά και [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.webz.gr/2008/12/17/%cf%84%ce%bf-%ce%bd%ce%ad%ce%bf-wordpress-27-coltrane-%ce%ba%ce%b1%ce%b9-%cf%84%ce%b1-%cf%83%cf%87%cf%8c%ce%bb%ce%b9%ce%b1/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Το νέο WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” και τα Σχόλια | Webz</a> on December 17, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23364\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] is the place to let you know that WordPress 2.7 is out, and it’s even easier to use than any version, ever. I’ve upgraded one of my sites to [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://mattherrebout.com/2008/12/wordpress-27-is-out/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 is Out | Denver Web Design, SEO and Web Marketing + Denver Photographer</a> on December 17, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23365\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane”Upgraded all of my sites today. How could I not, with a name like \"Coltrane\"? Let me know if anything seems off key.Tags: none     Tags: del.icio.us [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.chipsquips.com/?p=1566\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Chipping the web: December 17th -- Chip’s Quips</a> on December 17, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23366\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] diseño totalmente renovado, todo más a la mano, si quieres saber más a fondo puedes ir al mismo blog de wordpress y ver el vídeo con las nuevas [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.kcxlife.net/blog/2008/12/17/actualizaciones-varias/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Actualizaciones varias - kcxlife.net</a> on December 17, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23367\">\r\n	<p>[...] another painless website back-end update, this time from WordPress 2.6 (aka ‘Tyner’) to 2.7 (aka ‘Coltrane’). One of the additions to this version is the ability to automatically [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.skoardy.com/2008/12/18/wordpress-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 : Skoardy.com</a> on December 18, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23368\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress 2.7 [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://geekcast.fm/archives/geekcast-48-steve-jobs-is-sick-of-macworld/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">GeekCast 48: Steve Jobs is Sick of MacWorld : GeekCast.fm</a> on December 18, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23369\">\r\n	<p>[...] Not much really going on that’s worthy of note, I’ll make a rant about Telstra’s latest little tantrum tommorrow but for now, I suppose to stumbling around the internet will have to entertain you people. Although for those of you with blogs, and using wordpress, go update to 2.7, there’s some really cool stuff that’s been added in, check it out <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/</a> [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://anotherworthlessblog.net/2008/12/18/just-passin-through/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Just passin through… | AnotherWorthlessBlog</a> on December 18, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23370\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] can read the more detailed explanation written by Matt Mullenweg here.   Subscribe to comments Comment | Trackback   Post Tags: dashboard, upgrade, WordPress [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://wpmagz.com/2008/12/wordpress-27-is-out-get-it-now/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 is out! Get it now! - WPMagz.com</a> on December 18, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23371\">\r\n	<p>[...] 2008, under Uncategorized    After several weeks trying to use WordPress 2.7 beta-3 finally Final WordPress 2.7 is available. WordPress 2.7 has the code name Coltrane as usual, the developer of WordPress love [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://histla.com/wordpress-27-final-has-been-released.htm\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 Final has been released | histla.com</a> on December 18, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23372\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] reading and viewing all the good stuffs on the latest WordPress version, i decided to follow the crowd and upgrade my WordPress version to [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://mssheepy.com/archives/385\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Upgraded WordPress to 2.7 - Life Selections</a> on December 18, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23373\">\r\n	<p>[...] todos os sentidos – para terem idéia, mais de 150 pessoas mexeram diretamente no código. Segundo o blog oficial, além do novíssimo visual, que deve permanecer intacto até o final de 2009, o WP 2.7 marca uma [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://meublog.org/2008/12/18/novo-wordpress-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">MeuBlog.org » Blog Archive » Novo WordPress 2.7</a> on December 18, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23374\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] 遅ればせながら、Wordpressを２．７に。 この新しいバージョンは、コルトレーンと名付けられました。 もちろん、あのジョン・コルトレーンから採られた名前。 [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.overcube.com/wordpress/archives/1847\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress2.7は、コルトレーン | AZ::Blog</a> on December 18, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23375\">\r\n	<p>[...] interface comme ses nouveautés. Pour faire simple, nous allons donc simplement traduire l’article de présentation officiel par M