e. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.cult-f.net/2008/12/22/migrate-from-wordpress/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Cult-foo » How to migrate from WordPress.com to WordPress.org</a> on December 22, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23410\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress 推出 2.7 版本. 本文链接:2008年十大开源故事 4次阅读    « 收到 Gmail [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://losefoc.us/2008/12/22/top-10-open-source-stories-of-2008/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">2008年十大开源故事</a> on December 22, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23411\">\r\n	<p>[...] beautiful and intuitive backend interface. And many useful new features like the threaded comment:  WordPress › Blog » WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane”  Have you upgraded?    __________________ Read the [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.webmastermalaysia.com/blogging-discussion/16360-wordpress-2-7-coltrane-out.html#post83345\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 Coltrane is out! - Webmaster Malaysia Forum</a> on December 22, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23412\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] Reading on this… [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://prudenttrader.com/howto/?p=3\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” « How to Build Membersip Site</a> on December 22, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23413\">\r\n	<p>[...] long awaited new version of WordPress was released just over a week ago and I have got to say that I am really impressed with the new [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.peeledcarrots.com/2008/12/22/wordpress-27-coltrane-released/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” released - Peeled Carrots</a> on December 22, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23414\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] 听说2.7好像变了不少哦，果然一后台，排版什么的都变了，紧凑了不少吧，眼前一亮的感觉。。。不过这样子会不会就不简洁了呢？到官网去看看，说是出了中文网了嘢，good。本来还想耐着性子看E文版的2.7介绍的，现在有中文介绍的，潇洒多了，嘿嘿。真的有一个不得不提的功能：“自动升级 WordPress 功能，以后你将不用再重复下载、解压、上传文件的步骤，WordPress会自动帮你完成。”这个实在是贴心啊。还有“线程化可分页评论”这个就还不知道什么意思。。。还是慢慢来吧，这次好像整合了不少之前一些插件的功能哦，不错。 [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://blog.fallhua.de/2008/12/22/248/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">感觉挺不错啊wordpress2.7 | Home:Morning</a> on December 22, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23415\">\r\n	<p>[...] daha fazlası için wordpress.org bloguna [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://trrczx.com/?p=6\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 Çıktı! « TRrcZX - Blog</a> on December 22, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23416\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] opdateringer, men det skulle nu være løst. Resten af opdateringerne kan læses/ses via linket her.      « Jule-update [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://skallebank.dk/?p=503\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Jule-update #21 at Skallebank.dk</a> on December 22, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23417\">\r\n	<p>[...] el vídeo de presentación de la versión 2.7 que han publicado la gente de [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.zonical.net/blog/?p=80\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Zonical » WordPress 2.7 liberado!</a> on December 22, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23418\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] upgraded my version of WordPress today.&nbsp; WP 2.7 was announced 11 days ago after some pretty extensive research and development.&nbsp; Here’s the new dashboard [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.wongside.com/brian/blog/2008/12/wordpress-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Brian @ Wongside » Blog Archive » WordPress 2.7</a> on December 22, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23419\">\r\n	<p>[...] there’s a whole video on the new [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://superduperfant