\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23424\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress 2.7 was released – OK, maybe it happened slightly before I left, but still; I’ve had a little time to play around with it and so far it seems to be doing the job. The interface changes are welcome, and building in automatic upgrade and plug-in installation was a smart move. For the next version however, I think that if themes became installable from within WordPress, it would make a lot of people, including myself, happy. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://jonathandavies.org.uk/2008/12/24/what-did-i-miss/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">What Did I Miss? | Jonathan Davies</a> on December 24, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23425\">\r\n	<p>[...] Maybe you already know that WordPress 2.7 is now out because it has been blogged so many times. Currently, I can see 302 pings in the release post of this WordPress 2.7 or what they call “Coltrane“. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.awseome.net/welcome-wordpress-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Welcome WordPress 2.7 | Check it out here</a> on December 24, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23426\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” hat sich einiges unter der Haube getan. Unter anderem hat man die Auflistung der Kommentare in [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://3ckig.de/p141-wordpress-27-kommentare-formatieren/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7: Kommentare formatieren - eckig</a> on December 25, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23427\">\r\n	<p>[...] a WordPress hosted blog, you must be surely aware about the latest release of WordPress version – WordPress 2.7. Though the new version of WordPress is packed with loads of features, but still WordPress team [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.devilsworkshop.org/suggest-new-features-to-wordpress-team/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Suggest New Features to WordPress Team</a> on December 26, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23428\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] que es más facil de usar, además de que se pueden responder los comentarios desde el panel y muchas cosas más. WordPress [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.carlosleopoldo.com/post/wordpress-2.7/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Actualiza a WordPress 2.7</a> on December 26, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23429\">\r\n	<p>[...] und wartet mit sehr schönen Verbesserungen auf, die man sich schnell in einem Video auf der WordPress.org Seite reinziehen [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://luebecker-nachtleben.de/2008/12/11/wordpress-27-absolut-phantastisch.html\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 absolut phantastisch&nbsp;|&nbsp;Lübecker Nachtleben</a> on December 26, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23430\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] longer need to make adds up over time, improving productivity. A quote from the official WordPress version announcement page is shown [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://bosepro.info/support/site-upgrade-december/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">» Blog Archive » Site Upgrade (December)</a> on December 26, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23431\">\r\n	<p>[...] the site to WordPress 2.7 from 2.5, now that my broadband is back. (Is that worrying, that the first thing I think of [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.quiettrickster.co.uk/stuff/fangirl-for-wordpress\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">quiet trickster » Fangirl for WordPress</a> on December 26, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23432\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] Sisisi, puisque je te le dis! A l’occasion de la sortie encore et toujours améliorée de la version 2.7 (us) un mini tour du web de ses [..