ltrane-guts/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">ONAT LOPERA » Coltrane Guts</a> on December 29, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23438\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/ [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://golabs.nl/2008/10314/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 released at gooos.nl</a> on December 29, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23439\">\r\n	<p>[...] just upgraded the site software to the latest version of WordPress (2.7). They’ve changed the administration area entirely and it’s going to take a bit of getting used to! As always, if you spot any problems with the [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.iainlindley.co.uk/2008/12/29/wordpress-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 at Cllr Iain Lindley’s Diary</a> on December 29, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23440\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] Hvis dere vil lese mer:  <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/</a> [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.vardorussen.com/2008/12/oppdateringer-pa-gang/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Oppdateringer på gang | Vardørussen</a> on December 30, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23441\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress 2.7 was released [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://wp-community.org/2008/12/30/episode-49-wordpress-27-released-oxite-blog-world-expo-and-new-media-expo-to-merge-pownce-closes/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Episode 49: WordPress 2.7 released, Oxite, Blog World Expo and New Media Expo to merge, Pownce closes - The WordPress Community</a> on December 30, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23442\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] has had widgets for a while. I didn’t care much at first, but ever since I upgraded to version 2.7, I’ve been salivating for a new [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.oneofthewolves.com/2008/12/30/retrofitting-my-theme/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">One of the Wolves » Retrofitting My Theme</a> on December 30, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23443\">\r\n	<p>[...] Link to the release post at WordPress.org <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/</a> [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://blog.philsmith300.com/3228/upgrade-wordpress-27-coltrane/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Philsmith300’s Blog » Upgrade - WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane”</a> on December 30, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23444\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] dust hasn’t even settled on the exciting release of WordPress 2.7 yet they’re asking us to vote on the features for version 2.8. The most exciting one on the [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://zodomatica.com/wordpress-tips/blogs-about-wordpress/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Zodomatica - Bits of Tzaddi\'s Life</a> on December 30, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23445\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress Coltrane [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.zenelements.co.uk/blog/we-have-new-bits-2008/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Zen Elements Blog | We have new bits!??</a> on December 31, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23446\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] 1. Potential switch to WP 2.7. This could mean … avatars. <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/</a> [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.k-dot.ca/?p=460\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">k-dot » Work in Progress (also known as: kdot vs css)</a> on December 31, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23447\">\r\n	<p>[...] about three weeks ago&nbsp;a new version of WordPress was launched: WordPress 2.7.&nbsp; This new version contains cool new functions and features that I honestly can’t wait to [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.folaji.com/2008/12/31/upgrade-to-wordpress-27-coming-this-week/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Folaji.com » Blog Archive » Upgrade to WordPress 2.7 Coming This Week</a> on December 31, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23448\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] disponible la versión final de WordPress 2.7 que como ya se ha estado contando durante este tiempo trae muchas novedades. Más de 150 personas han estado trabajando en el código de esta nueva versión que ya se puede [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.kinexy.com/wordpress-27-%e2%80%9ccoltrane%e2%80%9d-disponible\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane”, disponible | Kinexy</a> on December 31, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23449\">\r\n	<p>[...] There may be some bugs yet to work out, but the interface is pretty slick. Take a tour of the new features here. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://hostomni.com/2008/12/upgraded-mmm-to-wp-27-coltrane/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Modelermagic help annex hostomni.com » Upgraded MMM to WP 2.7 “Coltrane”</a> on December 31, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23450\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] durante a tarde de hoje, devido à actualização do blog para a ultima versão do WordPress (WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane”). Embora a maior parte das alterações tenha ocorrido a níivel interno, contamos convosco para [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://otakupt.com/sem-categoria/wordpress-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7</a> on December 31, 2008</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23451\">\r\n	<p>[...] Just found time to update to the latest WordPress 2.7. This version has may new features under the hood. With the revamped admin interface, nearly every task you do on your blog will&nbsp;take fewer clicks and be faster&nbsp;in 2.7 than it did in a previous version. Another neat feature is&nbsp;the new dashboard that you can arrange with drag and drop to put the things most important to you on top. A few other important features include&nbsp;QuickPress, comment threading, paging, and the ability to reply to comments from your dashboard, the ability to install any plugin directly from WordPress.org with a single click, and sticky posts. With all these cool new features, it’s time to update your wordpress installs. Here is a video of the new features which was posted on the wordpress blog. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://abhinandh.com/wordpress-27-and-random-stuff/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 and random stuff… at Abhinandh - News, views, reviews and ofcourse Rants!</a> on January 1, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23452\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] los que mantenemos varios sitios webs construidos sobre diferentes productos. Al lanzamiento de wordpress 2.7 tenemos que sumar las actualizaciones, estas por motivos de seguridad, de las versiones 6.8 y 5.14 [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://blog.unlugarenelmundo.es/2008/12/13/drupal-68-y-phpbb-304/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Drupal 6.8 y phpBB 3.0.4 : Un lugar en el mundo…</a> on January 1, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23453\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress was gave this information about available WordPress 2.7 final which has a code name as Coltrane. WordPress.com was changed into this new version before, so if you are user on wordpress.com will [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.my-tutorialz.com/new-version-of-wordpress-27-has-already-to-download-for-your-own-hosting.html/\" rel=\"external nofollow