ess-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7.x &amp; new theme | David Poblador Garcia</a> on February 25, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23531\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress’ Blog says: “We heard how tired you were of doing upgrades for yourself and your friends, so now WordPress includes a built-in upgrade that will automatically notify you of new releases, and when you’re ready it will download them, install them, and upgrade your blog with a single click.” [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.ipassion.it/2008/12/12/whats-new-in-wordpress-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">What’s new in WordPress 2.7 | iPassion</a> on February 27, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23532\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] a huge fan of the commenting improvements introduced in WordPress 2.7. It’s a tremendous boon to have first-class threaded commenting features right out of the [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.chromakode.com/2009/02/wordpress-cancel-reply-button/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Hack: WordPress cancel reply button « chromakode</a> on February 28, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23533\">\r\n	<p>[...] you want to know more about the latest version and how to use it, try this post, introducing the ‘Coltrane’ upgrade’ on the wordpress site.   This entry was written by aharris and posted on March 1, 2009 at 7:00 pm [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://blogs.unimelb.edu.au/blog/2009/03/01/upgraded-to-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">University of Melbourne Blogs » Upgraded to 2.7</a> on March 2, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23534\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] De acordo com o WordPress Download Counter, WordPress 2/7 foi descarregado 1872184 vezes desde 10 de dezembro de 2008. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://criacaodesitesbrasil.wordpress.com/2009/02/16/wordpress-271-released/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7.1 Released « Criação de SItes</a> on March 8, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23535\">\r\n	<p>[...] February 10, 2008 WordPress is pleased to announce the immediate availability of WordPress 2.7.1. <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/development/2009/02/wordpress-271/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://wordpress.org/development/2009/02/wordpress-271/</a> [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://dev3.cre8tivestate.com/archives/1489\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7.1 Released (maintenance version) | Cre8tive State v2</a> on March 9, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23536\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] December 11, 2008 WordPress is pleased to announce the immediate availability of WordPress 2.7 [Coltrane]. <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/</a> [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://dev3.cre8tivestate.com/archives/863\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 Release | Cre8tive State v2</a> on March 9, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23537\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress 2.7 has been released. And I&nbsp;absolutely&nbsp;love it! The admin is very clean, workflow is much better and it just looks [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://danalog.nl/wordpress/wordpress-27-and-fluidapp/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 and Fluid.app - danalog.nl</a> on March 20, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23538\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] 2.7 is now&nbsp; live and available for download. Mark Jaquith just announced that.So officially WordPress 2.7 is out now.The new version has been named as ‘Coltrane’ for famed jazz saxophonist John [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://tech-mania.com/2008/12/wordpress-27-is-here/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 out | Tech Mania</a> on March 21, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23539\">\r\n	<p>[...] Yesterday marked the release of the next version of WordPress. WordPress 2.7, codenamed “Coltrane” has a completely redesigned admin interface, and is notably faster than WordPress 2.6.The admin dashboard can be rearranged by dragging and dropping the widgets to the location that you like. You can also shrink the widgets with the click of a button to clear more space on the main page. The admin menu on the left side of the dashboard can be changed from icons and text links, down to just icons to free up additional space on each page. There is also a new “Screen Options” that allows you to customize every admin page. On the write page, you are able to drag and drop everything in the right side column into the main column and have a full screen posting area.One more thing about the WordPress 2.7.. You will never have to manually upgrade WordPress 2.7 again. 2.7 has a built-in upgrade system that notifies you of a new release, and then when you request it to, will download, install, and upgrade your blog to the new version in a single click.On a side note, over 150 people contributed code towards this release. For more information on WordPress 2.7, visit the official WordPress Blog Post.Screenshots [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://dev.chrisjohnston.org/wordpress-27-released\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">chrisjohnston.org | WordPress 2.7 Released</a> on March 22, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23540\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] with the search engines regarding content as it is createdon the website. With WordPress, and 2.7 Coltrane, setting up a sitemap is a 5 minute affair, easy as [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.brandingmechanics.com/?p=11\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Setting Up XML Sitemaps for WordPress | Branding Mechanics</a> on March 24, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23541\">\r\n	<p>[...] I want give you update that all of my&nbsp;Free WordPress Themes&nbsp;are support and compatible with&nbsp;WordPress 2.7. Some of them also support Thread Comment featured that only avaliable in WordPress 2.7. Here some [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://riportag.com/?p=22\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Riportag | Turkey test</a> on March 30, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23542\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] told that WordPress 2.7 is easy to navigate.&nbsp; Only a few clicks and you’re ready to start writing your post.&nbsp; While [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://watershedstudio.com/blog/2009/04/wordpress-mindreader-plugin/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress MindReader Plugin | Watershed Studio, LLC | Indianapolis, Indiana</a> on April 1, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23543\">\r\n	<p>[...] a detailed explanation of the upgrade, please follow this [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.wilmink.eu/?p=38\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Weblog Sander Wilmink » Blog Archive » Upgrade Version 2.7.1</a> on April 2, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23544\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] ha lanzado WordPress 2.7 en su versión final lo que significa que ya puedes descargarlo desde el sitio oficial, por cierto, esta vez el CMS ha sido bautizado como [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://mundologia.net/2008/12/por-fin-wordpress-2-7-disponible-para-descarga\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Por fin! WordPress 2.7 disponible para descarga » Mundología</a> on April 3, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23545\">\r\n	<p>[...] the release of WordPress 2.7 and its near universal acceptance by users, I thought it time to reexamine a few of this [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://lewiszhang.com/2008/12/12/the-new-facebook-in-hindsight/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">/var/log/lzhang » Blog Archive » The New Facebook in Hindsight</a> on April 13, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23546\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] päivittyy toukokuussa WordPressin uuteen versioon 2.7. Päivitys tuo mukanaan sekä uusia ominaisuuksia että joitain muutoksia päivitysympäristön [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://blogs.helsinki.fi/blog/2009/04/21/blogipalvelu-paivittyy-wordpressin-versioon-27-pikaopas-kayttajille/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">- Blogipalvelu päivittyy WordPressin versioon 2.7 - Pikaopas käyttäjilleBlogipalvelut</a> on April 21, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23547\">\r\n	<p>[...] have been tested to be fully compatible with the latest WordPress release as well as WordPress MU and [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://blogs.praized.com/product/praized-plugins-version-20-lightbox-log-in-facebook-connect-and-more/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">The Praized Media Product Blog » Blog Archive » Praized Plugins Version 2.0: Lightbox Log-in, Facebook Connect and more</a> on May 4, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23548\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p><strong>Sick of compliment spam on your blog?…</strong></p>\r\n<p> One of the great things about having a blog is getting comments on your posts.  It’s particularly gratifying when someone takes the time to tell you that your post was helpful, entertaining, or well-written.<br>\r\nSpammers know this and exploit it b…</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Trackback from <a href=\"http://www.jasonmorrison.net/content/2009/sick-of-compliment-spam-on-your-blog/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">JasonMorrison.net</a> on May 31, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23549\">\r\n	<p>[...] beta 2 kemudian disusul dengan versi RC mulai dari RC 1 sampai RC 2. WordPress ini diklaim dalam blog nya akan memudahkan user dengan mengurangi klik yang dilakukan [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://masdeka.web.id/wordpress-27-resmi-direlease/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 resmi direlease | Catatan Pengalaman Hidup Programmer</a> on June 2, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23550\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] was still version 2.3.1 last year around this time, and now it’s 2.7, codename Coltrane. Who’s Coltrane. The biggest change in this version is the almost totally new interface. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://insennity.com/?p=608\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” | Insennity^</a> on June 27, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23551\">\r\n	<p>[...] 等了这么久，终于等到了WordPress 2.7 正式版发布，发表完这篇日志，我就着手将Sino Blog 正式升级到2.7 版本。 [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.sinoblog.org/2008/12/wordpress-27-release.html\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 正式版发布了 - Sino Blog</a> on June 29, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23552\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] that aside, I’m once again, and as always, excited by the spanking new release of WordPress with a shiny new [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://malaysiatube.net/blog/?p=87\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">What’s Your Most Favorite Feature in WordPress 2.7?</a> on July 10, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23553\">\r\n	<p>[...] I know many of you use wordpress for your blogs…if you havn’t heard yet, wordpress 2.7 has been released. It’s a major update with many imporvements. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.reubenland.com/2008/wordpress-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">reubenland.com » Blog Archive » WordPress 2.7</a> on July 12, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23554\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] 13, 2009, 0:51 This news item was posted in WordPress category and has 0 Comments so far. L’annonce vient d’être faite ce matin. Les gars de WordPress ont mis à disposition la version 2.7 [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://kerweb.olympe-network.com/wordpress/?p=38\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Kerblog » WordPress 2.7 Coltrane disponible !</a> on July 21, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23555\">\r\n	<p>[...] their blog they got a demonstration video, very like a normal play movie  available in HD too. AKPC_IDS += [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.xaviermedia.com/webbing/webbing/2008/12/13/wordpress-27-coltrane/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">» WordPress 2.7 \"Coltrane\" » XavierMedia.com</a> on July 28, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23556\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] by admin on December 10, 2008     While that wasn’ t ideal, and I especially sympathize with those of you creating books or tutorials around WordPress, there’s good news . The changes to WordPress in 2.5 and 2.7 were necessary for us to break free of much of the legacy cruft … that had built up over the years (gradually) and more importantly provide us with a UI framework and interface language we can use at the foundation to build tomorrow’s WordPress on, to express ideas we haven’ t been able to before. …   Here is the original: WordPress › Blog » WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://id.rapidshoots.com/wordpress-%e2%80%ba-blog-%c2%bb-wordpress-2-7-%e2%80%9ccoltrane%e2%80%9d/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress › Blog » WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” | Rapid Shoots Journey</a> on August 12, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23557\">\r\n	<p>[...] is aangekomen bij versie 2.7: Coltrane.Download [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://strikdiploma.nl/habari/wordpress-27-%25e2%2580%259ccoltrane%25e2%2580%259d\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” - My Habari</a> on August 19, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23558\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] is aangekomen bij versie 2.7: Coltrane.Download [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://strikdiploma.nl/wordpress-27-%25e2%2580%259ccoltrane%25e2%2580%259d\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” - S t r i k d i p l o m a . n l</a> on August 19, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23559\">\r\n	<p><strong>WordPress 2.7 적용 완료!…</strong></p>\r\n<p>Release Candidate 2가 출시되기가 무섭게 곧바로 정식 버전이 출시되었다.<br>\r\n무려 ‘Coltrane’ 이란 슈퍼스타의 이름을 따서 발매된 이번 버전은 이름이 아깝지 않을만큼 멋지다 ㅠㅠ<br>\r\n확 바뀐 대쉬보드는 꼭 다른 툴을 이용하고 있는것 같은 느낌을 주기도…….. 까진 아니지만 어쨌든 디자인도 훨씬 세련되어졌고 사용상의 편리함 또한 전 버전과 비교가 안된다.<br>\r\n개인적으로 가장 기대하던 개선된 댓글 …</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Trackback from <a href=\"http://www.goonerholic.net/?p=302\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">GOONERHOLIC</a> on August 19, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23560\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] [Update] WordPress.org homepage has the information about the release. I was indeed referring to the WordPress Official Blog which somehow didnt have the information while i was typing the post. The info is now up on the wordpress blog. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://technofriends.wordpress.com/2008/12/11/wordpress-27-is-now-available-for-download/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 is now available for Download. « Technofriends</a> on August 22, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23561\">\r\n	<p>[...] czwartek, z lekkim opóźnieniem, został opublikowany system blogowy WordPress 2.7, którym na marginesie odwala czarną robotę na mojej [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://banas.ovh.org/?p=352\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 | HOME OF bns</a> on August 25, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23562\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress was recently upgraded to version 2.7; therefore, here, I will be mentioning themes that are WordPress 2.7+ compatible [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://dukunoke.byethost13.com/wpp/?p=9\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Web - Art 77 » Blog Archive » Free WordPress (2.7) Themes .</a> on September 2, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23563\">\r\n	<p>[...] ^  WordPress › Blog&nbsp;» WordPress 2.7 “Coltrane” [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.sitweb.ro/2009/09/versiuni-wordpress/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Versiuni WordPress | Sit web</a> on September 7, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23564\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress was recently upgraded to version 2.7; therefore, here, I will be mentioning themes that are WordPress 2.7+ compatible [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://dukunoke.byethost13.com/wpp/?p=25\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Free WordPress 2.7+ Themes « Web - Art 77</a> on September 13, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23565\">\r\n	<p>[...] 16, 2008 · Leave a Comment  I just finished the ugprade to WordPress 2.7. I was more careful than usual given the big update (normally I just overwrite the files, this time [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://zzamboni.wordpress.com/2008/12/16/wordpress-27/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress 2.7 « zzamboni.org</a> on September 28, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23566\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] As you all know, WordPress 2.7 has been released. You can read about it’s features here. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.cult-f.net/dev/2008/12/22/migrate-from-wordpress/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">How to migrate from WordPress.com to WordPress.org « Cult-foo</a> on September 29, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23567\">\r\n	<p>[...] to the public. For more information on this extensive enhancement and bug-fix release, read the Development Blog and see theChangelog for [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://seo.girliza.com/2009/10/02/wp-2-7-new-features-en/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">wp 2.7 New Features « Girliza\'s profile</a> on October 1, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23568\" class=\"altc\">\r\n	<p>[...] WordPress 2.7. [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://mapumedia.de/17/und-dann-war-da-noch/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">Und dann war da noch…</a> on October 7, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n	<li id=\"comment-23569\">\r\n	<p>[...] Find the details about new Coltrane release please visit <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://wordpress.org/development/2008/12/coltrane/</a>  [...]</p>\r\n	<p><cite>Pingback from <a href=\"http://www.myhtmlworld.com/wordpress/wordpress-upgraded-coltrane.html\" rel=\"external nofollow\" class=\"url\">WordPress Coltrane | Sunils blog</a> on October 15, 2009</cite> </p>\r\n	</li>\r\n\r\n\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-3\">\r\n	<div class=\"blog-categories\">\r\n		<h4>See Also:</h4>\r\n		<p>For more WordPress news, check out the <a href=\"http://planet.wordpress.org/\">WordPress Planet</a>.</p>\r\n		<p>There’s also a <a href=\"http://wpdevel.wordpress.com/\">development P2 blog</a>.</p>\r\n		<p>To see how active the project is <a href=\"http://core.trac.wordpress.org/timeline\">check out our Trac timeline</a>, it often has 20–30 updates per day.</p>\r\n		<h4>Categories</h4>\r\n		<ul>\r\n				<li class=\"cat-item cat-item-14\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/news/category/releases/\" title=\"View all posts filed under Releases\">Releases</a> (109)\r\n</li>\r\n	<li class=\"cat-item cat-item-1\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/news/category/uncategorized/\" title=\"View all posts filed under Uncategorized\">Uncategorized</a> (94)\r\n</li>\r\n	<li class=\"cat-item cat-item-5\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/news/category/development/\" title=\"View all posts filed under Development\">Development</a> (89)\r\n</li>\r\n	<li class=\"cat-item cat-item-12\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/news/category/meta/\" title=\"View all posts filed under Meta\">Meta</a> (31)\r\n</li>\r\n	<li class=\"cat-item cat-item-3\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/news/category/community/\" title=\"View all posts filed under Community\">Community</a> (30)\r\n</li>\r\n	<li class=\"cat-item cat-item-15\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/news/category/security/\" title=\"View all posts filed under Security\">Security</a> (26)\r\n</li>\r\n	<li class=\"cat-item cat-item-7\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/news/category/events/\" title=\"View all posts filed under Events\">Events</a> (23)\r\n</li>\r\n	<li class=\"cat-item cat-item-18\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/news/category/testing/\" title=\"View all posts filed under Testing\">Testing</a> (20)\r\n</li>\r\n	<li class=\"cat-item cat-item-22\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/news/category/wordcamp/\" title=\"View all posts filed under WordCamp\">WordCamp</a> (16)\r\n</li>\r\n	<li class=\"cat-item cat-item-129\"><a href=\"http://wordpress.org/news/category/user-interface/\" title=\"View all posts filed under User Interface\">User Interface</a> (14)\r\n</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','WordPress 2.7 \"Coltrane\"',0,'','publish','open','open','','wordpress-27-coltrane','','','2013-05-25 18:31:13','2013-05-25 18:31:13','',0,'http://wp-archive.local/2.7.0/?p=3',0,'post','',0),(4,1,'2013-05-25 18:31:07','2013-05-25 18:31:07','','WordPress 2.7 \"Coltrane\"',0,'','inherit','open','open','','3-revision','','','2013-05-25 18:31:07','2013-05-25 18:31:07','',3,'http://wp-archive.local/2.7.0/?p=4',0,'revision','',0);
